Class CatalogCommands

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.codice.ddf.commands.catalog.CommandSupport
      • org.codice.ddf.commands.catalog.SubjectCommands
        • org.codice.ddf.commands.catalog.CatalogCommands
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.apache.karaf.shell.api.action.Action
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CqlCommands, DescribeCommand, ImportCommand, IngestCommand, InspectCommand, LatestCommand, RangeCommand, RemoveAllCommand, SpatialCommand, TransformersCommand

    public abstract class CatalogCommands
extends SubjectCommands
    Parent object to all Catalog Commands. Provides common methods and instance variables as well as the extension of org.apache.karaf.shell.console.OsgiCommandSupport and SubjectCommands that Catalog Commands can use.
    Author:
    Ashraf Barakat, ddf.isgs@lmco.com
